snippet.title: Abracadabrew - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
🦇   Coming October 14th!   🎃
➡️   Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1233250/Abracadabrew

Abracadabrew is a memory-based 1-4 player local couch co-op game. Cooperate with friends while using your memory skills to brew as many potions as you can before dawn. Gather ingredients hidden around the room while communicating and staying focused to unlock new brain-racking potions.
